'''Audison''' is one of the brands of  the Italian company [https://www.elettromedia.it Elettromedia s.r.l.], a manufacturer of [[Vehicle audio|car audio]] products. The company was founded in 1979, but Audison name (born from Latin words Audio and Sonus) was registered in 1984. Currently Audison has different kinds of [[mobile audio]] products: [[amplifiers]], [[Audio signal processing|audio processors]], [[loudspeaker|speakers]] and [[subwoofer]]s.

Audison has won numerous awards for sound quality{{citation needed|date=March 2018}} as well as “amplifier” of the year awards (EISA and CES awards).{{citation needed|date=March 2018}} The brand also counts many "Firsts" in its history: first amplifier with adjustable gain controls, first to build a dedicated mono block bass amplifier, first 5 channel amplifier.{{citation needed|date=March 2018}}

